                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>N Orls</placeName>\n                <date>May 8. 5611</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My dear friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I believe I have not as yet<lb/> acknowledged yours of <date>Feby\n                    19.</date> and<lb/> in good earth even more I have nothing<lb/> worthy of time\n                to write to you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I send you by mail to day the<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Picayune</hi> of last <date>Saturday 3d.</date> Inst<lb/> in\n                which you will find the paragraph<lb/> which I enclose for fear that the<lb/>\n                newspaper may not reach you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Our mutual friend <persName>Gutheim</persName> asked<lb/> me to\n                write a few lines about<lb/> you and have it inserted in the<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Picayune</hi> which I did with pleasure,<lb/> and the thought\n                just came to me<lb/> that he asked me to send you a copy<lb/> of the paper. Perhaps\n                he may have<lb/> also sent the paper.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As to your late congregation,<lb/> or a majority of them, I hold\n                them<lb/> in too little esteem even to say<lb/> a few words about them. Let<lb/>\n                them alone and their insignificance</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3v40kk4q/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
